{"tid":1478620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"拎豬嘴大陸仔落晒黎都係我818會堅守和理非既原因","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:09:48.000Z","uid":101623,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c963c60ce685a2a61c49b6e2e2bb4083f965646e","tid":1478620,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"我知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>就算我話<br />\n我一手朋友就係<br />\nblk左幾十個拎豬嘴黑衫大陸仔既海關<br />\n你地都未必會信</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔係想散布白色恐怖<br />\n818係一定要岀黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我想講既係<br />\n當日一定要100%提高警覺同理性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我而家預想到幾種班大陸哩可以用既手段</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>第一</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地可以自己由最基本，<br />\n砌鐵馬Set防線開始做起<br />\n同時間會不停鼓動人一齊同佢set防線<br />\n<br />\n<strong>第二</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然佢地會主動話要衝，<br />\n要去某啲政府機構示威<br />\n狗屋走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果示威者唔落搭</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能佢地會話<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">2019年！仲唔衝等乜啊！</span><br />\n煽動我地前線既手足<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果我地真係咁忍到手</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地可以自組幾個小隊自己開始做野<br />\n輕質胡亂叫囂<br />\n重質同狗對峙<br />\n重重質主動攻擊放火爆玻璃<br />\n<br />\n<strong>又或者再狗啲</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又安排假記者護旗手乜都好<br />\n今次會捉住佢地打到佢地半死<br />\n<br />\n<strong>若果我地真係仲可以保持到全和理非</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗佢地會主動攻擊我地既手足⋯<br />\n迫我地還擊<br />\n<br />\n除左襲擊手足我唔知點防之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其餘所有技倆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要818堅守純和理非，<br />\n就可以不攻自破</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>我地完全不受煽動，<br />\n問題就會迎刃而解<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong> 呢個係我堅守當日<br />\n一定會堅守和理非既原因<br />\n無論點都好<br />\n手足們打醒萬二分精神啦</strong>"},{"pid":"dbc84e82a2f9ad247d1c4808a040011e5c6368a4","tid":1478620,"uid":53612,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"818 係 和理優 ，和理優 只識9行企<br />\n勇武休息 <br />\n其他行為 入25 警數<br />\n警 有乜事 入 國安 數"},{"pid":"1ea2810fd403c42232e6acab2fa825f125f03b70","tid":1478620,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc84e82a2f9ad247d1c4808a040011e5c6368a4","tid":1478620,"uid":53612,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"818 係 和理優 ，和理優 只識9行企<br />\n勇武休息 <br />\n其他行為 入25 警數<br />\n警 有乜事 入 國安 數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"岩！！！！"},{"pid":"4a547c461760000f2abf6c0878f953bfb7785a28","tid":1478620,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b099cd15ad4a9db44ee2d8cd9e8ffd706f532ccf","tid":1478620,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2e2b4389034eeb6c38dc788d6e3c4a81f6c270f","tid":1478620,"uid":235796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"818講雞腸！"},{"pid":"075d946a296a27b391b83d95ce7ec1df6eba5f08","tid":1478620,"uid":105888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"818講英文！"},{"pid":"c471bab0a260d75d08cb29a174fa587f4ad5924b","tid":1478620,"uid":305349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1db3c7654995acedaa311b2ae632562531d193","tid":1478620,"uid":294052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"頭先去完攬炒巴集會上96